OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773907468
OL,3,CTwo men charged in relation to 'spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran'
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged in relation
OL,7,Fto spying for Iran on locations and
OL,8,Findividuals linked to the Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity, police have said.
OL,11,FNematollah Shahsavani, a dual Iranian
OL,12,Fand British national aged 40, and
OL,13,FAlireza Farasati, an Iranian national
OL,14,Faged 22, have both been charged with
OL,15,Fengaging in contact likely to assist a
OL,16,Fforeign intelligence service between
OL,17,FJuly 9 and August 15 last year.
OL,19,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,20,Fsaid Iran was the country the charges
OL,21,Frelated to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
