PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773907468
OL,3,CTwo men charged in relation to 'spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran'
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police said the men
OL,7,Fwere arrested and detained on Friday,
OL,8,FMarch 6, as part of an investigation
OL,9,Finto alleged surveillance of locations
OL,10,Fand individuals linked to the Jewish
OL,11,Fcommunity in the London area.
OL,13,FShahsavani, of Sandringham Gardens in
OL,14,FNorth Finchley, north London, and
OL,15,FFarasati, of Sandringham Gardens in
OL,16,FEdgware, north-west London, are due to
OL,17,Fappear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
