PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773907468
OL,3,CTwo men charged in relation to 'spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran'
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, head of the CPS
OL,7,Fspecial crime and counter-terrorism
OL,8,Fdivision, said: "We have decided to
OL,9,Fprosecute two men for an offence under
OL,10,Fthe National Security Act."
OL,12,FHe added: "The charge relates to
OL,13,Fcarrying out activities in the UK such
OL,14,Fas gathering information and
OL,15,Fundertaking reconnaissance of targets.
OL,17,F"The country to which the charge
OL,18,Frelates is Iran.
OL,26,@pD@QOUrD@[O]tD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
