PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773907468
OL,3,CTwo men charged in relation to 'spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran'
OL,6,F"We have worked closely with the
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Command at the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police as they have
OL,9,Fcarried out their investigation.
OL,11,F"We remind all concerned that criminal
OL,12,Fproceedings against these defendants
OL,13,Fare active and that they have the
OL,14,Fright to a fair trial.
OL,16,F"It is vital that there should be no
OL,17,Freporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,18,Finformation online which could in any
OL,19,Fway prejudice these proceedings."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@aO]
