OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Vicki
OL,12,FEvans, senior national co-ordinator
OL,13,Ffor counter-terrorism policing, said:
OL,14,F"These are extremely serious charges
OL,15,Funder the National Security Act, which
OL,16,Fhave come about following what has
OL,17,Fbeen a very complex investigation.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
