FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773907468
OL,3,CTwo men charged in relation to 'spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran'
OL,6,F"Since the men were arrested two weeks
OL,7,Fago, detectives have been working
OL,8,Faround the clock to gather and assess
OL,9,Fthe evidence, and we have liaised
OL,10,Fclosely with colleagues in the CPS to
OL,11,Freach this point.
OL,13,F"We fully recognise that the public `
OL,14,Fand in particular the Jewish community
OL,15,F` will be concerned but I hope this
OL,16,Finvestigation reassures them that we
OL,17,Fwill not hesitate to take action if we
OL,18,Fidentify there may be a threat to
OL,19,Ftheir safety, and will be relentless
OL,20,Fin our pursuit of those who may be
OL,21,Fresponsible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
