OL,3,CTwo men charged in relation to 'spying
OL,4,Con Jewish community for Iran'
OL,6,F"Counter Terrorism Policing work
OL,7,Fclosely with front-line officers
OL,8,Facross the country to keep communities
OL,9,Fsafe.
OL,11,F"Any concerns from the public can be
OL,12,Fshared with local policing teams or
OL,13,Fvia national reporting tools such as
OL,14,Fgov.uk/ACT."
OL,16,FPolice said two other men were
OL,17,Farrested on March 6 as part of the
OL,18,Finvestigation and have been released
OL,19,Fwithout charge.
